---
const _updated = '2026-06-19'
---

<BaseLayout title="Disclaimer — Blog" description="What blog.oriz.in is and isn't." hideSidebar={true}>
  <header class="page-head">
    <p class="eyebrow"><a href="/">Blog</a> / <a href="/legal/">Legal</a> / Disclaimer</p>
    <h1>Disclaimer</h1>
    <p class="meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
  </header>

  <article class="prose">
    <p>
      Everything published on blog.oriz.in is offered in good faith for general
      information only. Use it at your own risk.
    </p>

    <h2>Not financial advice</h2>
    <p>
      Posts in finance / cards / FIRE categories show calculators and reference
      data. They are not investment, tax, or insurance advice. Returns are
      computed from inputs, not predictions. Consult a SEBI-registered
      investment advisor before making financial decisions.
    </p>

    <h2>Not medical advice</h2>
    <p>
      Anything related to health is for general awareness. It is not a
      substitute for consultation with a registered medical practitioner.
    </p>

    <h2>Not legal advice</h2>
    <p>
      Articles touching on tax, regulation, or compliance reflect the author's
      reading of the rules at the time of writing. Rules change. Verify with
      your own counsel before acting.
    </p>

    <h2>External links</h2>
    <p>
      We link to third-party sites we find useful. We don't control their
      content, and inclusion is not an endorsement.
    </p>

    <h2>Affiliate disclosure</h2>
    <p>
      Where applicable, posts may earn a referral fee when you sign up to a
      service via certain links. This never affects what we recommend, and any
      such links are marked.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-head { padding-block: 3rem 1.5rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border); max-width: var(--container-prose, 720px); margin-inline: auto; }
  .eyebrow { color: var(--color-fg-muted); font-size: 0.8125rem; margin: 0 0 0.5rem; }
  .eyebrow a { color: var(--color-fg-muted); text-decoration: none; }
  h1 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 2.75rem); font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: -0.02em; margin: 0; }
  .meta { color: var(--color-fg-soft); font-size: 0.875rem; margin: 0.5rem 0 0; }
  .prose { padding-block: 2.5rem 4rem; color: var(--color-prose); line-height: 1.7; font-size: 1.0625rem; max-width: var(--container-prose, 720px); margin-inline: auto; }
  .prose h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.375rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--color-fg); margin: 2rem 0 1rem; }
  .prose p { margin: 0 0 1.25rem; }
  .prose a { color: var(--color-accent); }
</style>
